<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Data Pengunjung</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-image: url('/images/kolren.jpg'); 
            background-size: cover; 
            background-position: center; 
            background-attachment: fixed; 
            color: white; 
        }

        h1, h2 {
            font-size: 1.5em;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2em;
        }

        img {
            display: none; 
        }

        form {
            margin: 20px;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); 
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        input, button {
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-size: 1em;
        }

        button {
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        li {
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Daftar Pengunjung Kolam Renang</h1>
    <h2>Daftar Sekarang! Bergabunglah dengan kami untuk mendapatkan akses lebih mudah ke informasi penting dan fitur eksklusif.</h2>

    <form action="/users" method="POST">
        <label>Nama:</label><br>
        <input type="text" name="nama" required><br>
        <label>Email:</label><br>
        <input type="email" name="email" required><br>
        <label>No Telepon:</label><br>
        <input type="text" name="noTelp" required><br>
        <button type="submit">Tambah Pengunjung</button>
    </form>

    <h2>Pengunjung</h2>
    <ul>
        <% users.forEach(user => { %>
            <li>
                <strong><%= user.nama %></strong> (<%= user.email %>) - <%= user.noTelp %>
                <a href="/users/<%= user.id %>/edit">Edit</a> |
                <form action="/users/<%= user.id %>" method="POST" style="display:inline;">
                    <input type="hidden" name="_method" value="DELETE">
                    <button type="submit">Hapus</button>
                </form>
            </li>
        <% }); %>
    </ul>
</body>
</html>

